values.activities: ASCIE: Association of Graduate Students in Computer Information Science and Engineering
values.notes:
Coursework: Advanced Data Structures,Analysis of Algorithms,Computer Networks, Computer Communication,  Distributed Operating System Principles, Computer Architecture ,Database Management System, Software Engineering, Software Testing & Verification

Projects: 
Leader Election Algorithm: Implemented multithreaded distributed election algorithm to dynamically elect network topology leader using  multicast-based minimum spanning tree.

MIPS Disassembly and Simulation: Developed disassembler and designed a cycle accurate simulator to model out of order MIPS processor

Airline flight reservation system: Developed a website for  online air ticket reservation

Data Structures: Implemented & conducted performance  analysis of various operations on Red back trees , AVL trees & B trees

Gatorfone System: Implemented  VOIP based system by refining Linphone & integrating Asterisk & A2 Billing into it. Created a web portal to manage Gatorfone user accounts, user activities and billing information

values.activities: Presented paper on “Seamless Roaming- Future of Mobile Computing” at 20th student convention, Computer Society of India.
values.notes:
Coursework: Data structures, Computer organization, Operating systems, Data communication, Mobile communications, Software practice & testing, Data mining and warehousing, Logic design, Microprocessors

Academic Projects:

Steganography with encryption in video files: Implemented Java based two-fold data security mechanism by embedding RSA, Base-64 encrypted text files in video files and obfuscating them using LSB addition technique.
